        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "(1) Whether the proposed collection of information is necessary for the proper performance of ACL's functions, including whether the information will have practical utility;",
        "bbox": [
          0.07294117647058823,
          0.2733333333333333,
          0.3427450980392157,
