      {
        "id": "mineru_newspaper_bf784eedb0c377adb9a0f286954af785_2_21",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "se FoodanD Administration (FDA or Agency) is announcing the availability ofa final guidance for industry entitled \"COvID- 19: Developing Drugs and Biological Products for Treatment or Prevention.\" This guidance describes FDA's current recommendations regarding phase 2 or phase  trias for dugs or bilogical products under development for the treatment or prevention of COVID–19. Given the public health emergency presented by COVID–19, this guidance document is being implemented without prior public comment because FDA has determined that prior public participation is not feasible or appropriate, but it remains subject to comment in accordance with the Agency's good guidance practices.",
        "bbox": [
          0.3615686274509804,
          0.7018181818181818,
          0.6298039215686274,
          0.9363636363636364
        ],
        "order": 18
      }
    ]
  },
  {
